object.customQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT 
prkr.policy_system_id as policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_number as policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number as policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key as policy_key,
prkr.policy_key_code as policy_key_code,
prkr.risk_system_id as risk_system_id,
prkr.risk_id as risk_id,
l.system_id as loss_history_system_id,
l.id as loss_history_id,
l.cmm_container as loss_history_record_type,
l.risk_id_ref as risk_id_reference_number,
l.loss_cause_cd as prior_carrier_loss_cause,
l.loss_dt as prior_carrier_loss_date,
l.claim_number as prior_carrier_claim_number,
l.carrier_name as prior_carrier_name_sourced_from_loss_history,
l.policy_type_cd as prior_carrier_policy_type,
l.source_cd as prior_carrier_source,
l.paid_amt as prior_carrier_paid_indemnity_amount,
l.expense_amount as prior_carrier_paid_expense_amount,
l.reserve_amount as prior_carrier_reserve_amount,
l.subrogation_amount as prior_carrier_subrogation_amount,
l.claim_status_cd as prior_carrier_claim_status,
l.loss_desc as prior_carrier_loss_description,
l."comment" as prior_carrier_comment,
l.claim_type_display as prior_carrier_claim_type ,
l.reported_by as loss_history_reported_by,
b.homeautocreditdescription as companion_auto_carrier_and_policy_number,
a.systemid as application_system_id,
a.applicationnumber as application_number,
t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_id as prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_id,
t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_md5_hash_value  
FROM dbo.loss_history_stg l
LEFT JOIN dbo.building_stg b
ON l.system_id = b.systemid
AND l.cmm_container = b.cmmcontainer
AND l.risk_id_ref = b.parentid
left join dbo.basicpolicy_stg bs 
on l.system_id = bs.systemid 
and l.cmm_container = bs.cmmcontainer 
LEFT JOIN dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
ON l.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
AND l.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
AND l.risk_id_ref = prkr.risk_id
LEFT JOIN dbo.application_stg a
ON  bs.originalapplicationref = a.systemid
left join dbo.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss t
on t.loss_history_id = l.id
and t.loss_history_system_id = l.system_id 
and t.loss_history_record_type = l.cmm_container 
and t.risk_id = prkr.risk_id 
and t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_effective_end_date  = '9999-12-31'
WHERE prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date  = '9999-12-31'
UNION
SELECT 
DISTINCT 
prkr.policy_system_id as policy_system_id,
prkr.policy_number as policy_number,
prkr.policy_module_number as policy_module_number,
prkr.policy_key as policy_key,
prkr.policy_key_code as policy_key_code,
prkr.risk_system_id as risk_system_id,
prkr.risk_id as risk_id,
l.system_id as loss_history_system_id,
l.id as loss_history_id,
l.cmm_container as loss_history_record_type,
l.risk_id_ref as risk_id_reference_number,
l.loss_cause_cd as prior_carrier_loss_cause,
l.loss_dt as prior_carrier_loss_date,
l.claim_number as prior_carrier_claim_number,
l.carrier_name as prior_carrier_name_sourced_from_loss_history,
l.policy_type_cd as prior_carrier_policy_type,
l.source_cd as prior_carrier_source,
l.paid_amt as prior_carrier_paid_indemnity_amount,
l.expense_amount as prior_carrier_paid_expense_amount,
l.reserve_amount as prior_carrier_reserve_amount,
l.subrogation_amount as prior_carrier_subrogation_amount,
l.claim_status_cd as prior_carrier_claim_status,
l.loss_desc as prior_carrier_loss_description,
l."comment" as prior_carrier_comment,
l.claim_type_display as prior_carrier_claim_type ,
l.reported_by as loss_history_reported_by,
b.building_application_home_auto_credit_description as companion_auto_carrier_and_policy_number,
a.systemid as application_system_id,
a.applicationnumber as application_number,
t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_id as prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_id,
t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_md5_hash_value 
FROM dbo.loss_history_stg l
LEFT JOIN dbo.building_application_stg b
ON l.system_id = b.building_application_system_id
AND l.cmm_container = b.building_application_cmm_container
AND l.risk_id_ref = b.building_application_parent_id
LEFT JOIN dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
ON l.system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
AND l.cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
AND l.risk_id_ref = prkr.risk_id
LEFT JOIN dbo.application_stg a
ON  l.system_id = a.systemid
AND l.cmm_container = a.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss t
on t.loss_history_id = l.id
and t.loss_history_system_id = l.system_id 
and t.loss_history_record_type = l.cmm_container 
and t.risk_id = prkr.risk_id 
and t.prior_carrier_and_prior_loss_row_effective_end_date  = '9999-12-31'
WHERE prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date  = '9999-12-31'
